\v 24 Y <a name="01403302400004" ll="SDBH:קשׁר:000008">conspiraron</a> <a name="01403302400006">contra</a> <a name="01403302400006">él</a> <a name="01403302400008" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000">sus</a> <a name="01403302400008" ll="SDBH:עֶבֶד:000000">siervos</a>, y lo <a name="01403302400012" ll="SDBH:מות:000001">mataron</a> en <a name="01403302400016" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000">su</a> <a name="01403302400016" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000">casa</a>. 
